Release Info:

An incredibly exciting truck game

To rule the road, you will have to be the best  Truck Racer gives you the
opportunity to drive and customize plenty of trucks in order to take part
of crazy races through four solo modes(championship, time attack,
elimination, quick race). You can also play with friends (2 players offline
and 4 players online). Ride through smoke and danger to become the new king
of the road

10 environments and 48 tracks
6 truck categories with distinct styles, and 54 possible upgrades
A championship mode with 13 events
2 multiplayer modes : up to 2 players offline and 4 players online
Realistic and localized damages

Notes

Enjoy This Fine COMPLEX Release
